summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eastlake Avenue from Almy Street to the north margin of Tuhrman Avenue et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 19242, creating Local Improvement District No. 1849 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
